Big Lots is a discount department store, with over 1,400 locations, providing top brand merchandise and quality products at incredible deals. Big Lots’ assortment includes discount furniture, such as home décor and bedding, seasonal patio and outdoor décor, as well as grocery and national brand products at closeout prices. 
